    "body": "### Language server\n\n_No response_\n\n### Requested feature\n\nExpose floating window config through setup. \r\n\r\nWith my current theme, the borders aren't visible, making it hard to read the window's contents. Thanks to [this snippet](https://github.com/williamboman/nvim-lsp-installer/issues/475#issuecomment-1037222808), I've enabled rounded borders. Would feel less of a hack if it was officially supported at setup.\r\n\r\n**Before**\r\n\r\n![borders-invisible](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/4924405/153713923-26d7fa88-3f9f-4afb-b429-1064a2a3facc.png)\r\n\r\n**After**\r\n\r\n![borders-visible](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/4924405/153713947-7582710b-ffcc-4c67-abed-2dfad745f1b8.png)\n\n### Other clients which have this feature\n\n_No response_",
